{"tid":2123443,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(奶共) 荷里活幫中國打倒美國！《怪醫D老篤》帶挈中國戲院重開成功。","createTime":"2020-07-24T15:29:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T16:13:36.000Z","uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ed3f47b854723e442af72054e8546c6a415a69e3","tid":2123443,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T15:29:45.000Z","msg":"美國電影業媒體Deadline早前報導: 中共加速重開戲院, 企圖跑贏美國.  荷里活亦應承全力幫中共，安排多套美國大片在中國上映托市.<br />\n<br />\n結果，真係成功左。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《怪醫D老篤》係中國近4000間戲院上映，首日開畫票房勁收840多萬人仔。考慮到中國戲院只可開放３０％坐位，《怪醫D老篤》票房數字係好撚勁。　<br />\n<br />\n荷里活而家全力幫中共重開戲院，如果美國疫情持續，戲院再唔重開，<strong>中國極可能成為今年最高戲院票房既國家，取代美國多年來既霸主地位。</strong>　<br />\n中共在政治公關戰又贏美國。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />　（荷里活竟然願意將電影王國地位讓比中國。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/54Gm0LU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F54Gm0LU.jpg&h=2f231371&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d0211f62aba9369c7e0af7aa0adfaad1397e096","tid":2123443,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T15:30:25.000Z","msg":"美國電影業媒體Deadline:<br />\n<br />\n- 大陸戲院重開, 快過美國.<br />\n<strong>- 消息人士指大陸戲院的重開步伐將會非常快.</strong><br />\n- 多套美國大片將陸續上映托市.<br />\n<br />\n- 學者Stanley Rosen分析<br />\n1) <strong>中共加快戲院重開, 為證明自己的防疫措施是世界頂級.</strong><br />\n2) 大陸戲院成功重開, 中共將獲不少國際媒體大讚, 贏盡面子.<br />\n3) <strong>香港疫情再爆而要封戲院, 反而大陸戲院可加快重開,  這讓中共更加有體面. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n4) 台灣防疫獲國際讚賞, 戲院也已重開.  中共以台灣作目標, 自然也要加快戲院重開, 不能在面子上輸給台灣.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/DeadlineNancy/status/1283909161458098181\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDeadlineNancy%2Fstatus%2F1283909161458098181&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxRVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=87bc5e78\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDeadlineNancy%2Fstatus%2F1283909161458098181&h=79f3f17d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/DeadlineNancy/status/1283909161458098181</a>"},{"pid":"b23374343f113a2d7d929df99c6e626645cb67e3","tid":2123443,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T15:32:23.000Z","msg":"如果荷里活奶共奶得盡D, 分分鍾會安排《TENET天能》係中國搶先全球上映. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67eb9be588a3225b1cbbeb7da315f6824da40398","tid":2123443,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b23374343f113a2d7d929df99c6e626645cb67e3","tid":2123443,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T15:32:23.000Z","msg":"如果荷里活奶共奶得盡D, 分分鍾會安排《TENET天能》係中國搶先全球上映. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T15:35:41.000Z","msg":"美國抗中共, 其實唔易<br />\n<br />\n好多有錢佬企係中共果邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f34477194fdf0c1527cc4b738805a49269e8691c","tid":2123443,"uid":292497,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T15:36:59.000Z","msg":"果套好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d8e5fe253a4eabaa8768d173e1eb7e2b8e6ccf1","tid":2123443,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f34477194fdf0c1527cc4b738805a49269e8691c","tid":2123443,"uid":292497,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T15:36:59.000Z","msg":"果套好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T15:39:26.000Z","msg":"但食正大陸觀眾口味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e566bd8ea7f1abbf6869a63b0a956ad1fc360df","tid":2123443,"uid":62749,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T15:39:3